%% Diagram: FairPlay SPC/CKC key exchange
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Application
    participant FPS as FairPlay framework (OS)
    participant SE as Secure Enclave
    participant KSM as Key Security Module (License server)

    App->>FPS: load HLS playlist with EXT-X-KEY skd://content-id
    FPS->>SE: derive session key, build SPC
    SE-->>FPS: SPC blob (device id + content id + nonce, encrypted to Apple)
    FPS-->>App: SPC
    App->>KSM: POST SPC (+ user entitlement)
    KSM->>KSM: validate SPC, lookup content key, apply policy
    KSM-->>App: CKC (content key wrapped to session)
    App->>FPS: provide CKC
    FPS->>SE: unwrap CKC, install content key
    SE-->>FPS: key bound to hardware path
    FPS-->>App: playback proceeds
